{"tid":1145410,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【支爆近了】阿里巴巴拖網站公司數6個月？","createTime":"2019-05-08T16:40:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T21:33:51.000Z","uid":79317,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ed1464c4cf07be91d57d685ec95d791a95560df4","tid":1145410,"uid":79317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T16:40:31.000Z","msg":"早兩日見阿里巴巴係香港搞電競比賽有得報名<br />\n一入網站<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JqKTjk2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJqKTjk2.jpg&h=f7df5e2b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n諗住隔幾日會改好，依家係BLANK PAGE<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.wesg.com.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wesg.com.hk%2F&d=fyMqA0bs77BZF9qEbHCyfkYD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=27b6258c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.wesg.com.hk/</a><br />\n但FACEBOOK繼續賣緊有比賽打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n百度：&quot;阿里体育成立于2015年9月，由马云掌控的阿里巴巴控股，新浪和云峰基金共同出资&quot;<br />\n阿里體育同其他業務有無關定獨立 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n侵侵一出手，九龍新界無得走<br />\n騰訊會唔會跟住出事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4373957326eaa6439b8da161e5e481230746d408","tid":1145410,"uid":113373,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T16:40:55.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捍衛香港 終局之戰<br />\n反對修訂逃犯條例</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">5月11日 星期六 早上8點半 <br />\n立法會將會開會討論有關修訂 暫未知會否表決 <br />\n由於秘書處政變 原本由涂謹申主持會議改為石禮謙主持<br />\n<br />\n事態危急<br />\n一定要阻止立法<br />\n否則香港直送中國受審<br />\n到時中國話你犯咗中國法律 無需證據 無需理由<br />\n就可以光明正大係香港夾你返中國 <br />\n坐黑獄 洗你腦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">此修例禍害大於23條立法<br />\n23條&gt;&gt;&gt;(需危害國家安全，香港審判，香港監禁)<br />\n<br />\n修訂逃犯條例 &gt;&gt;&gt;(莫需有，中國政府可任意控告香港人任何罪行，香港會配合執法將你拘捕，移交中國審判及監禁，無需證據 無需理由)</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"4d9a8a91718faa6313dda21787fa52235c6588ed","tid":1145410,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T16:42:16.000Z","msg":"屌你正啊喂"},{"pid":"4c6cc36e8060188c820404ffe3ccc99da1010ac0","tid":1145410,"uid":106426,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T16:43:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f4818005a053ecceb6ed588a9fb134a2ad92ea20","tid":1145410,"uid":79317,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"4c6cc36e8060188c820404ffe3ccc99da1010ac0","tid":1145410,"uid":106426,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T16:43:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T16:48:33.000Z","msg":"隔幾日都仲係BLANK 無變正常<br />\n似拖緊數叫人換番白頁有事慢慢傾多D <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddcc1efedab766aab8b92f96ab20fcf0916335f0","tid":1145410,"uid":158283,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4373957326eaa6439b8da161e5e481230746d408","tid":1145410,"uid":113373,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T16:40:55.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捍衛香港 終局之戰<br />\n反對修訂逃犯條例</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">5月11日 星期六 早上8點半 <br />\n立法會將會開會討論有關修訂 暫未知會否表決 <br />\n由於秘書處政變 原本由涂謹申主持會議改為石禮謙主持<br />\n<br />\n事態危急<br />\n一定要阻止立法<br />\n否則香港直送中國受審<br />\n到時中國話你犯咗中國法律 無需證據 無需理由<br />\n就可以光明正大係香港夾你返中國 <br />\n坐黑獄 洗你腦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">此修例禍害大於23條立法<br />\n23條&gt;&gt;&gt;(需危害國家安全，香港審判，香港監禁)<br />\n<br />\n修訂逃犯條例 &gt;&gt;&gt;(莫需有，中國政府可任意控告香港人任何罪行，香港會配合執法將你拘捕，移交中國審判及監禁，無需證據 無需理由)</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T17:35:57.000Z","msg":"點解可以個個POST 霸到一樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71cfd289f5229342474ea7d76df1e21222ab435d","tid":1145410,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T17:57:47.000Z","msg":"CY?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2644c542f696ae5f0a